## Flow Comparison Matrix

| Flow Step | Railnova | SignatureRail | MMS-MFC Current | MMS-MFC Ideal |
|-----------|----------|---------------|-----------------|---------------|
| **Dashboard entry** | ✅ Cards | ❌ None | ✅ Cards | ✅ Keep |
| **Status filtering** | ✅ Click badge | ⚠️ Dropdown | ⚠️ Manual | ✅ Click badge |
| **Detail view** | ✅ Slide panel | ❌ New window | ⚠️ New page | ✅ Slide panel |
| **Gantt view** | ✅ Horizontal | ✅ Horizontal | ⚠️ Vertical | Consider both |
| **Create intervention** | ✅ Click timeline | ❌ Menu | ⚠️ Button | ✅ Click timeline |
| **Drag to schedule** | ✅ Supported | ✅ Supported | ❌ Missing | ✅ Add |

