## Priority Flows to Improve

### P0 - Critical
1. **Dashboard → Problem identification** - Add clickable status badges
2. **Detail view** - Add slide-out panel (avoid page navigation)

### P1 - Important
1. **Gantt interactions** - Add click-to-create
2. **Allocation view** - Consider Gantt-based approach

### P2 - Nice to Have
1. **Drag and drop** - For advanced scheduling
2. **Horizontal Gantt option** - Industry standard alternative

